    "description": "<p>Digie Engineering Technology Pte. Ltd. is a BIM specialist team who driven by innovation, to provide full range of BIM services to our clients and assist them to generate the maximum output with minimal cost. &nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Our services includes:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>BIM Resource Planning</li>\n  <li>BIM Execution Planning</li>\n  <li>BIM Implementation</li>\n  <li>BIM On-Site Support</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We apply the relevant technologies and guide industry professionals with the adoption of modern day design technologies to replace traditional building practices, so that our clients toward a smooth project transition without having to invest on additional in-house personnel and software.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>We provide strategic and technical advice to ensure better communication and collaboration amongst the project team.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>",
